  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/638470/extras/f8464ffeb42a9bf66ea81f5c9e3a399f.poster.avif?t=1760114894\" width=624 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/638470/extras/f8464ffeb42a9bf66ea81f5c9e3a399f.webm?t=1760114894\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/638470/extras/f8464ffeb42a9bf66ea81f5c9e3a399f.mp4?t=1760114894\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Eggggg is a ridiculous two-button platform game where you propel yourself around using your vomiting superpowers. </strong>Gilbert has an extreme allergy to eggs, and eating them will literally make him vomit like a fountain. He escapes from his mean Aunt Doris in order to get to a birthday party, and needs to use his vomiting superpower to survive in a world of angry cyborg chickens... of course.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/638470/extras/39d3a4991ff8c7fdcfdfc8b5b6ddcaa6.poster.avif?t=1760114894\" width=624 height=229 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/638470/extras/39d3a4991ff8c7fdcfdfc8b5b6ddcaa6.webm?t=1760114894\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><strong>Features:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A unique and fun platform runner suitable for both adults and kids<br></li><li>36 hand-crafted levels of vomiting action<br></li><li>Awesome and unique visual style by the Spanish illustrators Brosmind.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/638470/extras/421f4b5b178acd31a4d61f1895a5cd70.poster.avif?t=1760114894\" width=624 height=158 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/638470/extras/421f4b5b178acd31a4d61f1895a5cd70.webm?t=1760114894\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><strong>Controls</strong><br>If you're looking for just another normal platformer, this is not it. But if you're looking for a really fun and quirky experience, and enjoy a good challenge - give it a go! The controls are simple to use but hard to master. Once you get the hang of it, they offer really great and accurate control.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/638470/extras/7ada0981a844843241e957d392a8012f.poster.avif?t=1760114894\" width=624 height=173 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/638470/extras/7ada0981a844843241e957d392a8012f.webm?t=1760114894\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/638470/extras/f8464ffeb42a9bf66ea81f5c9e3a399f.poster.avif?t=1760114894\" width=624 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/638470/extras/f8464ffeb42a9bf66ea81f5c9e3a399f.webm?t=1760114894\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/638470/extras/f8464ffeb42a9bf66ea81f5c9e3a399f.mp4?t=1760114894\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Eggggg is a ridiculous two-button platform game where you propel yourself around using your vomiting superpowers. </strong>Gilbert has an extreme allergy to eggs, and eating them will literally make him vomit like a fountain. He escapes from his mean Aunt Doris in order to get to a birthday party, and needs to use his vomiting superpower to survive in a world of angry cyborg chickens... of course.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/638470/extras/39d3a4991ff8c7fdcfdfc8b5b6ddcaa6.poster.avif?t=1760114894\" width=624 height=229 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/638470/extras/39d3a4991ff8c7fdcfdfc8b5b6ddcaa6.webm?t=1760114894\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><strong>Features:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A unique and fun platform runner suitable for both adults and kids<br></li><li>36 hand-crafted levels of vomiting action<br></li><li>Awesome and unique visual style by the Spanish illustrators Brosmind.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/638470/extras/421f4b5b178acd31a4d61f1895a5cd70.poster.avif?t=1760114894\" width=624 height=158 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/638470/extras/421f4b5b178acd31a4d61f1895a5cd70.webm?t=1760114894\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><strong>Controls</strong><br>If you're looking for just another normal platformer, this is not it. But if you're looking for a really fun and quirky experience, and enjoy a good challenge - give it a go! The controls are simple to use but hard to master. Once you get the hang of it, they offer really great and accurate control.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/638470/extras/7ada0981a844843241e957d392a8012f.poster.avif?t=1760114894\" width=624 height=173 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/638470/extras/7ada0981a844843241e957d392a8012f.webm?t=1760114894\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>",
